title: Cinci You've Been Gone
description:
Mina talks to Arif Hasan of The Athletic about the four weirdest teams in the NFL. These teams all have a decent chance to make the playoffs, but Mina and Arif hash out whether or not they are actually any good. Plus, they dive into the latest MVP odds.
